title: Honey Sriracha Chicken Tenders
directions: Heat oven to 400Â°F and Spray large cookie sheet with cooking spray.
In small bowl, mix honey and Sriracha. In large resealable food-storage plastic bag, place bread crumbs.
Coat chicken with Sriracha mixture. Place in bread crumb bag; seal and shake to coat.
Bake 15 to 20 minutes, turning once, until chicken is no longer pink in center and bread crumbs are golden brown.
